255
00:12:17,987 --> 00:12:19,330
Ổn.

256
00:12:19,781 --> 00:12:22,534
- Bọn tớ đang làm quảng cáo cho Bud Super Bowl.
- Xin lỗi.

257
00:12:22,784 --> 00:12:24,707
- Khá hay.
- Hay đấy.

258
00:12:27,580 --> 00:12:28,797
